	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-4890">
		<article id="comment-4890" class="comment-body clearfix">
			<div class="comment_avatar">
				<img alt='Brent Waddell' src='//1.gravatar.com/avatar/a840daec3d2a84dfe8b5c0a71e727d59?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a840daec3d2a84dfe8b5c0a71e727d59?s=160&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-80 photo' height='80' width='80' loading='lazy'/>			</div>

			<div class="comment_postinfo">
				<span class="fn">Brent Waddell</span>				<span class="comment_date">
				on December 28, 2012 at 12:58 pm				</span>
